They took a whole different approach with this game form making it a RPG with platformer ellements into making it a platformer with RPG ellements. Also the visuals are way different and the storyline was alot more melodramatic than the other pm games.

They should have made this game a whole different concept than paper mario because people just compare it with the 1st 2 pm games, but i agree with u it was a fun game and perhaps people will stop comparing it and like it for what is and not what isn't.

@Brucie Kibbutz
I see your point, but I don't agree. Yes, there are many similarities, but to me those are all superficial elements. It didn't "feel" like a Zelda game to me, but of course that's very subjective.
Sorry if my comment sounded condescending, it wasn't my intention (English isn't my main language).
